{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-18",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_18_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 18 - The Fall-Guy",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 9,
  "page_start_sec": 497.05,
  "page_end_sec": 740.52,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.691,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 497.05,
      "end": 499.14,
      "text": "You won't need any of our help.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.256,
      "end": 502.18,
      "text": "\"'If that's what you think,' Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 502.76,
      "end": 504.52,
      "text": "\"'you haven't seen or heard enough.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.632,
      "end": 507.42,
      "text": "Gutman's good humor was undisturbed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 507.94,
      "end": 508.68,
      "text": "He remonstrated,"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.6,
      "end": 510.08,
      "text": "\"'Now come,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 510.32,
      "end": 510.54,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 510.6,
      "end": 511.08,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.52,
      "end": 513.3,
      "text": "you can't expect us to believe at"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.3,
      "end": 515.08,
      "text": "this late date that you are the least"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.2,
      "end": 516.5,
      "text": "bit afraid of the police,"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.7,
      "end": 519.25,
      "text": "or that you are not quite able to handle.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.16,
      "end": 522.22,
      "text": "Spade snorted with his throat and nose.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 522.84,
      "end": 523.52,
      "text": "He bent forward,"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.76,
      "end": 525.32,
      "text": "resting forearms on knees again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.58,
      "end": 527.38,
      "text": "and interrupted Gutman irritably."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.24,
      "end": 529.86,
      "text": "\"'I'm not a damn bit afraid of them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 529.98,
      "end": 531.56,
      "text": "and I know how to handle them."
    },
    {
      "start": 531.88,
      "end": 533.44,
      "text": "That's what I'm trying to tell you."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.14,
      "end": 536.38,
      "text": "The way to handle them is to toss them a victim,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 536.864,
      "end": 538.784,
      "text": "somebody they can hang the works on.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.46,
      "end": 539.96,
      "text": "\"'Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.04,
      "end": 540.36,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.54,
      "end": 543.3,
      "text": "I grant you that that's one way of doing it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.66,
      "end": 543.98,
      "text": "but—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.544,
      "end": 546.22,
      "text": "\"'But hell,' Spade said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.656,
      "end": 547.72,
      "text": "\"'it's the only way.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.94,
      "end": 551.18,
      "text": "His eyes were hot and earnest under a reddening forehead."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.88,
      "end": 554.0,
      "text": "The bruise on his temple was liver-colored.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 554.41,
      "end": 556.56,
      "text": "I know what I'm talking about."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.792,
      "end": 558.9,
      "text": "I've been through it all before,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 559.06,
      "end": 560.76,
      "text": "and I expect to go through it again."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.6,
      "end": 563.94,
      "text": "At one time or another I've had to tell everybody",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 563.94,
      "end": 566.06,
      "text": "from the Supreme Court down to go to hell,"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.48,
      "end": 567.6,
      "text": "and I've got away with it."
    },
    {
      "start": 568.14,
      "end": 570.48,
      "text": "I got away with it because I never let myself"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.48,
      "end": 572.38,
      "text": "forget that a day of reckoning was coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.82,
      "end": 575.4,
      "text": "I never forget that when the day of reckoning comes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.78,
      "end": 577.82,
      "text": "I want to be all set to march into headquarters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.4,
      "end": 579.92,
      "text": "pushing a victim in front of me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.96,
      "end": 580.22,
      "text": "saying,"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.62,
      "end": 580.72,
      "text": "Here,"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.1,
      "end": 581.58,
      "text": "you chumps,"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.74,
      "end": 582.62,
      "text": "here's your criminal."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.88,
      "end": 583.008,
      "text": "now."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.86,
      "end": 585.0,
      "text": "As long as I can do that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 585.16,
      "end": 588.0,
      "text": "I can put my thumb to my nose and wiggle my fingers at"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.0,
      "end": 589.08,
      "text": "all the laws in the book."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.88,
      "end": 591.2,
      "text": "The first time I can't do it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 591.28,
      "end": 592.26,
      "text": "my name's Mudd."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.66,
      "end": 593.64,
      "text": "There hasn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.64,
      "end": 594.64,
      "text": "been a first time yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.92,
      "end": 596.4,
      "text": "This isn't going to be it."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.248,
      "end": 597.94,
      "text": "That's flat.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 599.648,
      "end": 600.72,
      "text": "Kutma's eyes flickered,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 600.82,
      "end": 602.8,
      "text": "and their sleekness became dubious,"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.38,
      "end": 604.56,
      "text": "but he held his other features"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.7,
      "end": 607.08,
      "text": "in their bulbous pink smiling complacent cast,"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.36,
      "end": 609.48,
      "text": "and there was nothing of uneasiness in his"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.64,
      "end": 609.8,
      "text": "voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.06,
      "end": 610.98,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.86,
      "end": 614.68,
      "text": "\"'That's a system that's got a lot to recommend it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 614.76,
      "end": 614.92,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.12,
      "end": 616.38,
      "text": "By gad it has."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.22,
      "end": 617.72,
      "text": "And if it was",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 617.72,
      "end": 619.36,
      "text": "any way at all possible this time,"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.48,
      "end": 620.94,
      "text": "I'd be the first to say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.08,
      "end": 622.7,
      "text": "stick to it by all means,"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.78,
      "end": 623.04,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.98,
      "end": 626.98,
      "text": "But this just happens to be a case where it's not practical.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 627.968,
      "end": 629.28,
      "text": "That's the way it is with the best of",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 629.36,
      "end": 629.62,
      "text": "systems."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.06,
      "end": 632.76,
      "text": "There comes a time when you've got to make exceptions,"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.16,
      "end": 635.1,
      "text": "and a wise man just goes ahead"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.32,
      "end": 635.82,
      "text": "and makes them."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.1,
      "end": 636.82,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.92,
      "end": 637.14,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.35,
      "end": 639.32,
      "text": "that's just the way it is in this case,"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.42,
      "end": 641.12,
      "text": "and I don't mind telling you"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.2,
      "end": 644.04,
      "text": "that I think you're being very well paid for making an exception."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.14,
      "end": 645.64,
      "text": "Now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 645.82,
      "end": 646.92,
      "text": "maybe it will be a"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.92,
      "end": 648.72,
      "text": "little more trouble to you than if you had"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.72,
      "end": 650.5,
      "text": "your victim to hand over to the police,"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.66,
      "end": 651.56,
      "text": "but—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.24,
      "end": 652.76,
      "text": "He laughed"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.88,
      "end": 653.78,
      "text": "and spread his hands."
    },
    {
      "start": 653.96,
      "end": 657.06,
      "text": "\"'You're not a man that's afraid of a little bit of trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 657.43,
      "end": 658.4,
      "text": "You know how"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.52,
      "end": 659.24,
      "text": "to manage things,"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.48,
      "end": 662.66,
      "text": "and you know you'll manage to land on your feet in the end,"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.7,
      "end": 663.4,
      "text": "no matter what"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.56,
      "end": 663.78,
      "text": "happens."
    },
    {
      "start": 665.34,
      "end": 666.26,
      "text": "He pursed his lips,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 666.42,
      "end": 667.96,
      "text": "partly closing one eye."
    },
    {
      "start": 669.216,
      "end": 671.64,
      "text": "And maybe it might be that we could",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 671.64,
      "end": 673.94,
      "text": "add a little something more to what's in that envelope."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.584,
      "end": 677.42,
      "text": "Spade's eyes had lost their warmth.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 678.18,
      "end": 679.78,
      "text": "His face was dull and lumpy.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 681.14,
      "end": 682.5,
      "text": "We'll talk about the money later,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 683.16,
      "end": 684.0,
      "text": "he said in a low,"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.14,
      "end": 685.46,
      "text": "consciously patient tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 685.8,
      "end": 686.4,
      "text": "We're"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.56,
      "end": 687.96,
      "text": "talking about the police now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.2,
      "end": 688.92,
      "text": "or I am,"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.04,
      "end": 690.78,
      "text": "and I know what I'm talking about."
    },
    {
      "start": 691.94,
      "end": 692.32,
      "text": "This is my",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 692.52,
      "end": 693.68,
      "text": "city and my game."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.0,
      "end": 696.4,
      "text": "I could manage to land on my feet,"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.54,
      "end": 697.08,
      "text": "sure,"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.22,
      "end": 697.76,
      "text": "this time,"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.22,
      "end": 699.18,
      "text": "but the next time I tried"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.18,
      "end": 700.34,
      "text": "to put over a fast one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.52,
      "end": 702.96,
      "text": "they'd stop me so quick I'd swallow my teeth."
    },
    {
      "start": 703.86,
      "end": 704.34,
      "text": "Hell with that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 705.16,
      "end": 705.54,
      "text": "You birds",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 705.6,
      "end": 708.74,
      "text": "will be in New York or Constantinople or someplace else."
    },
    {
      "start": 709.568,
      "end": 710.784,
      "text": "I'm in business here.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 711.904,
      "end": 712.4,
      "text": "But surely,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 712.8,
      "end": 713.76,
      "text": "Gutman began,"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.28,
      "end": 714.38,
      "text": "you"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.12,
      "end": 715.74,
      "text": "can—I can't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 715.92,
      "end": 717.4,
      "text": "Spade said earnestly."
    },
    {
      "start": 717.92,
      "end": 718.54,
      "text": "I won't."
    },
    {
      "start": 718.56,
      "end": 719.36,
      "text": "I mean it."
    },
    {
      "start": 720.1,
      "end": 721.34,
      "text": "He sat up straight.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 721.888,
      "end": 724.62,
      "text": "A pleasant smile illuminated his face,"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.72,
      "end": 726.36,
      "text": "erasing its dull lumpishness."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.88,
      "end": 728.2,
      "text": "He spoke rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.4,
      "end": 729.44,
      "text": "in an agreeable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.48,
      "end": 730.42,
      "text": "persuasive tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.808,
      "end": 732.28,
      "text": "Listen to me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 732.34,
      "end": 732.52,
      "text": "Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.7,
      "end": 734.88,
      "text": "I'm telling you what's best for both of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.25,
      "end": 736.78,
      "text": "If we don't give the police a"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.78,
      "end": 737.16,
      "text": "fall guy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.38,
      "end": 740.52,
      "text": "it's ten to one they'll get news of the falcons sooner or later."
    }
  ]
}